dc_title_s: North Sea, Germany, the Weser, Nordenham to Farge (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "From a German chart of 1987." Not distributed to depository libraries. "Copyright 1998 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." Place names in German with glossary in English. "Soundings in meters." Includes 6 insets at varying scales. Map No. 37235. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
